 of air..When time stops, almost as if, seconds never mattered..In that moment, I am infinite..In that moment, I am immortal..In that moment, I am, finally, alive..', 23314, 0), (120226, 'Check your heart and make sure your intention steers you in the right direction.', 11007, 0), (120227, 'Even the strongest hearts can be fragile. It takes only seconds to hurt someone. But sometimes it takes years to repair the damage. Cherish the hearts that love you.', 12391, 0), (120228, 'True giving is not what goes on when the cameras are rolling-but what goes on in the heart.', 15872, 0), (120229, 'Imagine how differently you might approach each day by simply stating: God is good. God is good to me. God is good at being God. And today is yet another page in our great love story. Nothing that happens to you today will change that or even alter it in the slightest way.', 4427, 0), (120230, 'She had on a blue bonnet, and with a pair of lovely eyes of the same colour, has contrived to make me feel devilish odd about the heart.', 23315, 0), (120231, 'When you say to someone "follow your heart", it actually refers to the rhetorical representation of various emotions, that are precisely produced from neural activity of the limbic system.', 2874, 0), (120232, 'Photoshop and Lightroom help me transform my photos into what my heart felt, but my camera couldn''t quite capture!', 19365, 0), (120233, 'Always follow your brain, because your heart is dumb as shit', 23316, 0), (120234, 'The less gear you use, the more you grow as a photographer. Although there are fewer options available, you''ll find more creative ways to capture what you feel! In a way, all your technical options before turn into creative solutions that improve your photography even more.', 19365, 0), (120235, 'He started to estrange her... And they became strangers Who knew each other''s heart, So broken as they drifted apart.', 5065, 0), (120236, 'You read these thingsAnd you ask the world,Why doesn’t it happen To someone like you?Deep in your heart,You knew the answer:It’s because you don’t let it.', 23317, 0), (120237, 'And then she got a bad, bad feeling because she realized she had been wrong.You can fool a person.You can fool a dog.You can fool a cat or a horse or a teacher or a friend.But you cannot ever fool a heart.', 7698, 0), (120238, 'There is no real silence for the sensitive ears and there is no real tranquility for the sensitive hearts!', 3701, 0), (120239, 'Life is amazing beautiful when your vision flows through your heart before your eyes.', 23318, 0), (120240, 'The heart, I think, which is the home of all things rhythmic, is where learned poems go to live.', 8138, 0), (120241, 'Dance from the heart and let your passion shine through', 23319, 0), (120242, 'Dance from your heart and let your passion shine through', 23319, 0), (120243, 'There is a myth at the heart of things and some element of genius in the heart of each person.', 5018, 0), (120244, 'Why does it seem more difficult to heal a wounded ego than a wounded heart?Is it because the heart accepts the cold hard reality of rejection and tries to move on, while the ego has no capacity to act likewise?And while the heart weeps, the ego desires revenge: an eye for an eye, no matter what it takes?', 12184, 0), (120245, 'I''m going to ejaculate sparkles into your heart!', 23320, 0), (120246, 'He fell in love with her house and land,He fell in love with her pension plan,He worked his way to her lonely heart,He was quite wily from the very start.', 15872, 0), (120247, 'One stone is enough to break a glass, One sentence is enough to break a heart,One smile is enough to fall in love,& one God is enough to live a fulfilling life..', 23321, 0), (120248, 'For now, this afternoon, you saw and touchedmy heart, dissolved and liquid in your hands.', 20550, 0), (120249, 'May it always cost the head as long as it does not cost the heart', 23322, 0), (120250, 'Don''t strive to be beautiful from the outside, strive to be beautif