INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (120951, 'Little beat big When Little smart. First with the head, then with the heart.', 23419, 0), (120952, 'I once heard this saying that God keeps breaking your heart until it opens. And ain''t that the truth. Think about it. Every struggle, every challenge, every adversity brings you closer to your heart, to your true self, to who you really are. Sometimes you got to be broken down to the point where you feel powerless to discover your ultimate and true power.', 23420, 0), (120953, 'Ben is the kind of guy that reaches into your heart and possesses it.', 5279, 0), (120954, 'this heart yearns...for the salt of unsmelt airunswept thunderstorms...unknown adventures.', 1864, 0), (120955, 'My world is a million shattered pieces put together, glued by my tears, where each piece is nothing but a reflection of YOU.', 5935, 0), (120956, 'Never loan your heart to hatred', 23421, 0), (120957, 'The most magical thing I have come across is a beautiful face with a beautiful heart and it''s you❤ ❤', 23422, 0), (120958, 'I had crossed fifty years of my life, and come across uncountable females as son, husband, father, friend in my life. Coming across several women I carefully studied most of them, and feels that I got master knowing female. But every time when my heart comes across to a female, my all knowledge on female goes to a vain. What they want? , What are they looking for? When their mind changes? When their priority changes? No one knows, in a minute they use to change decisions, if someone ask, they says it’s a little thing. They never think, little things makes big or if they can’t stick on little things how they can stand in important decisions. They never show they are weak, but every time they are compromising themselves. It’s their big heart but impacting every around. They always think they can do anything by doing nothing.', 15753, 0), (120959, 'Only love can be shared endlessly and still your heart will 