me in. It will fill your mind and dance with your heart.', 2586, 0), (120988, 'Speak to the breeze cautiously during those lonely summer nights.', 6122, 0), (120989, 'Keep your heart open for love', 23427, 0), (120990, 'There is a song in your heart, only you can hear it. In silence, that is the song of longing and love.', 2586, 0), (120991, 'Your eyes are hallow,Your heart is bruised,Your temple has been raided,Your soul has been shattered,Was he worth it?', 8667, 0), (120992, 'I could watch her dance for hours, Because she''s always dancing inside of my heart.', 8667, 0), (120993, 'The desire to belong is in every mind.The desire to get lost in love is in every heart.', 2586, 0), (120994, 'When my heart is better, less shrunken, I will throw her out there to love again, without hesitation, even knowing what we know.', 23428, 0), (120995, 'To pray is to communicate with the essence. Praying is calling home.', 9207, 0), (120996, 'Feel, now let your heart be your light; imagination is your way and bliss is your destination.', 2586, 0), (120997, 'If you truly have compassion in your heart, show it by keeping your doubts to yourself and sharing your hope with those who love change!', 3301, 0), (120998, 'Anna’s conclusions were these: That fire is beautifully cruel. That fusion occurs only at a specific heat. That blood, in fact, can boil. That the dissolution of an affair is an entropic reaction, and the disorder it tends toward is flammable. That a heart will burn. And burn and burn and burn.', 18946, 0), (120999, 'I''m chasing a decade old ghost. Searching beneath the rafters of a cobweb-filled haven lined with old memories which my brain cannot accept are dead. The light of nostalgia is burning bright inside my heart. Ignoring the emptiness around me, and hoping for a resurrection of love.', 23426, 0), (121000, 'The stars, like the hollow eyes of a god forgotten, marry the sadness of the exhausted hour and inspire a little chaos, a little gentleness, to those below.