urs soar from dawn to dawn splitting your time Don’t hear melody from a soundless chime', 2760, 0), (121077, 'Pray GOD by HEART, Not by HABIT.', 5034, 0), (121078, 'To enjoy a peaceful & Beautiful Life We should open our ''EYE'' and Close our ''I', 5034, 0), (121079, 'We must live with our hearts in our hands - like Mary.We must hold the blood-red heart and no be disappointedwhen others look away.', 8853, 0), (121080, 'This isn''t a reasoned response to a configuration of stars, but the heart cannot flourish on logic alone. Unreason is an essential medicine as long as you don''t overdose', 591, 0), (121081, 'When the anesthesia of love wears off,you suffer the pain of consequence.', 1039, 0), (121082, 'One day, I decided I was going to write books forever.', 14195, 0), (121083, 'Crying is NOT a weakness. Cry as much as you have to. Don’t be afraid or ashamed to let your tears flow. Crying is a natural part of life. We all have feelings, and sometimes crying is all that we can do. Crying can help relieve the pain, hurt, disappointments, and all of the other things that life can throw our way. Know that it’s okay, and know that you’re going to be okay as well. Wishing You: Peace of mind, Comfort, Happiness, Joy within and LOVE.', 3491, 0), (121084, 'Prayer is a heart exercise. It’s an act of communicating with God about what’s most important and pressing in your life.', 4239, 0), (121085, 'Love is never blind; it sees with ucute clarity. A closed mind, wounded heart, and a bitter disposition surely cannot perceive love''s myriad ways of communicating.', 2747, 0), (121086, 'I don’t care what people think. I don’t care how many dislikes I get on Youtube. I don’t care how many people compare to every single female artist in the industry, because we’re both white and sing. I do this because I love it, and I do it because this is what I feel like I was born to do, I feel like I was born to write music to heal the world.', 23445, 0), (121087, 'my dear,we are all made of water. it''s okay to rage. sometimes it''s okay to rest. to recede.', 1864, 0), (121088, 'you are ever the only onei want to giveall the peachesin my heart tothe only one by whomi want them bruised.', 1864, 0), (121089, 'His mind was logical, but his traitorous heart stuttered from beat to beat.', 184, 0), (121090, 'When we follow our hearts, we follow the path of lessons we were meant to take and gain knowledge from. Sometimes the heart conquers over reason, and this may lead us to making serious mistakes, but these are mistakes written for us to grow. This is the real reason you hear ‘FOLLOW YOUR HEART’. And the real reason you hear, ‘FOLLOW YOUR DREAMS’ is because our dreams expose us to our true multidimensional realities outside of this delusional realm we call reality. Our true reality can be found in our dreams, where we are our true multidimensional selves.', 2678, 0), (121091, 'Be brave enough to never yearnFor that you cannot hold closeIn your heart forever.Tread lightly, cherish compassionAnd live in the moment without fear.', 23446, 0), (121092, 'What the eye doesn''t see, the heart doesn''t grieve about.', 23447, 0), (121093, 'Have and show motivation to do and learn. That''s the key for a good career. Everything else is an extrapolation of that.', 5034, 0), (121094, 'People may not like you, but that''s cool because your heart doesn''t beat from their liking. You can''t live to please everyone, you''re not a puppet', 3145, 0), (121095, 'Would you dare to reach inside the vault of a feral heart?Glare into the keyhole, eyes bound with intrigue...is it real what we perceive? or does the absent colour leave you lost or decieved?', 23448, 0), (121096, 'A stream of primal voicesWhispering in the breeze of your heartTo urge you on.', 23446, 0), (121097, 'If the tree doesn''t hug you back, it''s not a problem with the tree, it''s a problem with your heart.', 14553, 0), (121098, 'A sober mind, an unemotional heart and a positive attitude are key for success.', 23449, 0), (121099, 'Death is deceitful, pretending that peace is on the horizon. The truth is that chaos is left in its wake, claiming the souls of those stranded in life. Death is the enemy of love in its purest form. It''s the one thing that can tear our souls out and rip our hearts to pieces. The miraculous part of this process is that all it needs to do is extinguish a single, solitary breath. That''s all it takes to steal the future of someone; someone who deserves to live more than all the others. If only I could capture that breath before it was taken to replace it with my own.', 1154, 0), (121100, 'When does God turn a want into a need? When you feel the same way almost every day. Your thoughts can be distracted for a short period of time, but your mind will always take you back to the one place that feels like home.', 290, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (121101, 'Magic?" What did magic have to do with breaking into someone''s store and stealing their stuff?"Don''t you get it?" Peter said. "You''re free now. You don''t have to live by their rules anymore." Peter pointed into the inky blackness of the basement. "The darkness is calling. A little danger, a little risk. Feel your heart race, listen to it. That''s the sound of being alive. It''s your time, Nick. Your one chance to have fun before it''s all stolen by them, the adults, with their cruelty and endless rules, their can''t-do-this, and can''t-do-that''s, their have-tos, and better-dos, their little boxes and cages all designed to break your spirit, to kill your magic.', 1329, 0), (121102, 'I think the biggest achievement of my life is that I followed my heart when I knew what it wanted, and had faith in destiny when I didn''t know what it held.', 15408, 0), (121103, 'One should hold fast one''s heart; for when one letteth it go, how quickly doth one''s head run away!', 11, 0), (121104, 'Take off my clothes and there becomes a man. Take off my skin and there becomes my bones. Break all my bones and there becomes my heart. Smash my heart and there becomes my soul. And that you cannot take.', 23450, 0), (121105, 'To have been where you have beenAnd to still have joy,Dazzling in your heart,Now there’s a thing to make the whole world smile.', 23446, 0), (121106, 'Sometimes a loved one might not ''spit'' the message in the most tender or poetic fashion that suits you, but don''t allow a rugged style to blind you from a loving intent. It''s the spirit of the message one must receive beyond [the] perception of one''s senses; be mindful of hearing with the heart.', 2747, 0), (121107, 'Bettering the lives of others is the role of a person with a servant’s heart.', 4239, 0), (121108, 'Never be afraid to cry. Sometimes, nothing can cleanse the heart more than a few wet tears.', 14553, 0), (121109, 'The sacred bequestOf times long spent with your heartThat saturate and illuminate you nowSo piercingly…', 23446, 0), (121110, 'Doing things God’s way is always a matter of the heart.', 4404, 0), (121111, 'Spirituality can exists only in a pure heart.', 23451, 0), (121112, 'Every heart needs a cutting part sharper than a blade to stab agony', 2760, 0), (121113, 'If you Fear, your Heart will decay', 23448, 0), (121114, 'You can''t have a women''s body without having her heart, mind and soul if only momentarily.', 7743, 0), (121115, 'The unlikely group that resulted from the union of five diverse characters in their late twenties operated with surprising harmony. This cohesiveness could be attributed to two factors: 1) everyone’s issues and embarrassing pasts were plainly disclosed prior to the gang’s formation and 2) the clan had been expressly conceived as a male support group.', 5126, 0), (121116, 'Still not sure about how easily he could be integrated into their posse, Trevor smiled in delighted relief at how tolerantly two of his close friends had received his new identity.', 5126, 0), (121117, 'Tear your heart out of your chest. And hand it to God. There is no other healing. I swear, there is no other healing.', 10137, 0), (121118, 'The wound made by hurting with fire will heal but the wound created by harsh words uttered using out tongue leaves an indelible scar.', 4911, 0), (121119, 'They don’t know I only speak in runaway train stationsand everybody is always a few minutes too late to the platform.No one has ever gotten the chance to get too closebecause it is never romantic to fuck the girl who makes love to her own sadness every single night.', 23452, 0), (121120, 'They can stop a river by building a dam, but I will be damned if they can stop my river of blood flowing through my veins and heart.', 3341, 0), (121121, 'Theres no competition in DESTINY. Run your own RACE and wish others WELL!!!', 5034, 0), (121122, 'Be content to love, to dazzle in the light,If only for moments…And then be gone,With gladness in your heart,Before the creeping shadowsClaim too much your sadness at leaving.', 23446, 0), (121123, 'my heart no longer beats but is a tugging muscle,', 629, 0), (121124, 'You will find what you are looking for when you realize God has placed those longings in your heart as a divine desire', 23453, 0), (121125, 'Sanity is to the mind, insanity is for the heart,Docility is to the mind, wildness is to the heart,Tamable is the mind, Untamable is the heart,Freedom is to the mind, cages are for the heart.', 7743, 0), (121126, 'The only enemy which stands between the talent you posses and success you achieve is known as "EGO" in our Society', 5034, 0), (121127, 'The most important principle for self discovery and to taste success is rather than changing other''s attitude changes your own. And always remember same sun which melts the butter also hardens the clay', 5034, 0), (121128, 'I met a man; broken as can be, A smile upon his face; no shoes upon his feet,He said one thing " young one , you listen clear"The choices you make now; will always reappear,Live to your heart but do wrong to none,Because when your old like me; you''ll remember all you have done.', 3305, 0), (121129, 'Guard your heart and mind against double-minded pretentious beings. Do not allow infiltration beyond the surface. If their influence travels on the inside, they become like an incurable disease.', 3145, 0), (121130, 'The only way to be content in life is to make sure your NEED don''t become GREED.', 5034, 0), (121131, 'Begin each day with a positive thought and a grateful heart.', 3604, 0), (121132, 'I ache not from need -but from my heart''s gluttony of you.', 3691, 0), (121133, 'When the heart stops, you die. Love is everywhere that life is, and if there is no love for life, you die. Giving up on love is the same thing as giving up on life itself.', 251, 0), (121134, 'You cannot taste a song but you can feel the tune relishing your heart where strings of music belong.', 2760, 0), (121135, 'Step back in perspective, open your heart and welcome transition into a new phase of life.', 23454, 0), (121136, 'Open the doors of your heart and they will come…And for every cruel arrow,Sweet caresses of delirium alsoTo nourish your soul.', 23446, 0), (121137, 'Pursue what catches your heart, not what catches your eye.', 3604, 0), (121138, 'Pursue what catches your heart rather than what catches your eye.', 3604, 0), (121139, 'Could he hear my heart pounding?', 1421, 0), (121140, 'When we observe trials and tribulations in our world, there''s even more reason to lighten the heavy load. Sometimes life gets tough and it''s disheartening. Never mind happiness; what we genuinely need is joy! God didn''t intend for us to be sad or serious all of the time. His word in Proverbs 17:22 (ESV) says, “A joyful heart is good medicine, but a crushed spirit dries up the bones.', 7289, 0), (121141, 'Pursue what catches your heart rather than what catches your eyes.', 3604, 0), (121142, 'What is it that you long for best, that clenches teeth and claws over the ventricles of your heart?', 23455, 0), (121143, 'When people want to win they will go to desperate extremes. However, anyone that has already won in life has come to the conclusion that there is no game. There is nothing but learning in this life and it is the only thing we take with us to the grave—knowledge. If you only understood that concept then your heart wouldn’t break so bad. Jealousy or revenge wouldn’t be your ambition. Stepping on others to raise yourself up wouldn’t be a goal. Competition would be left on the playing field, and your freedom from what other people think about you would light the pathway out of hell.', 290, 0), (121144, 'A man that knows your worth doesn''t need to be told how to treat you. That''s a given! You won''t have to question his feelings, his motives, nor his intentions. How will I know? You ask. See, he will freely show you how he feels and prove it consistently. If you''re settling for anything less than what you deserve. Then, maybe you don''t even know your worth.', 3145, 0), (121145, 'I have worn my heart on my sleeve because it is too painful to carry it inside my chest.When I carry it on my sleeve, it has the freedom to exist, to beat in rhythm with the Universe.I feel like I''m more alive and yes, there are those who out of curiosity will say or do things that can cause its delicate existence to feel pain and sorrow.I would rather deal with that, than to put it back in its little cage where it knows nothing else but the rhythm of my body and my Ego.My heart was never meant to be part of my Ego.My heart was meant to experience the Soul.', 23456, 0), (121146, 'No body is a looser either he is a Winner or a Learner', 5034, 0), (121147, 'Being Wise & Being Smart are two different things anyone can be smart but those who master the art of knowing what to overlook in this journey called life deserves to be called Wise', 5034, 0), (121148, 'The only goal in life is to be happy, genuinely, intensely and consistently , regardless of what it looks like to others.', 5034, 0), (121149, 'But though you’d never starve your body to wasting and still expect to go on, you starve your heart, yet act as though you can still draw on it forever without the debt ever coming due. If you fall—when you fall, you’re going to fall like a starving man.', 1690, 0), (121150, 'Find answers in your weakness and surprise in your strength and always remember the golden rule every failure has HOPES', 5034, 0);
